formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1. The project was ongoing at the time of enactment of Real Estate Regulation and Development Act, 2016. So, numerous deposits from allottees and payments for the purpose of project were already affected at the time of commencement of the Act. Further, Management of the project was unable to open a separate bank account for the purpose of RERA for the same reason. Considering the problem faced by the management, it is difficult to deposit the amount received from allottees to a separate RERA Account.
2. However, on getting registration certificate from Real Estate Retulatory Authority (RERA) for registration of project, promotors have converted their existing current account in to RERA Account and details of said account has been furnished in the above table.
3. Earliear, all transactions were done from RERA Account specified above (i.e. 100%  of advance received from allottees were deposited in to this account and amount of all expenses were also withdrawed from this account) including deposit/withdrawals from promotoer's contributions and unsecured loans. However, Now as on the date of signing of this certificate, the promotors have opened separate bank account for the purpose of regular withdrawals (30%) Account. 
4. This certificate is prepared based on provisional books of accounts provided to us till 31.01
.2021.
5. As earliear discussed at note Note no. 2, the prmoters have converted existing current bank account in to RERA Account. Thus 70% of  advance received from customers has been shown as cumulative withdrawal in clause 7 above.
6.  In Annexure to CA Certificate (Form 3A), in the column "Date of Agreement of Sale",  date of Agreement of sale or Date of Sale deed as applicable in particular case is provided.
7.  In Annexure to CA Certificate (Form 3A), some units are booked where payment more than 10% has been receive, however Agreement to sale has not been executed. The management have given explanation that, allottee has given written request to Promotor that allottee is not sure about in whose name document to be executed, so till the name is  finalized do not execute the agreement to sale.
8.  In Annexure to CA Certificate (Form 3A), in the column"Mobile Number of Allottee" as per request of promoters, contact number of Promotor is provided due to security reasons.
